title: Grönwall's inequality
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Let $$a,b,w$$ be non-negative continuous functions on $$[t_0,t_0+c]$$ satisfying
$$
w(t) \le a(t) + \int_{t_0}^t b(s)w(s)\,\d s,\qquad t \in [t_0,t_0+c].
$$
Then we have:
$$
w(t) \le a(t) + \int_{t_0}^t a(s)b(s)\exp\left({\textstyle\int_s^tb(\tau)\,\d\tau}\right)\,\d s.
$$